{"tid":137501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港聞 【人口統計】你的人工全港排第幾？","createTime":"2017-02-28T00:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T06:12:09.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72983f1f3a8702492c6824d465e403b7605df742","tid":137501,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:43:19.000Z","msg":"對於許多打工仔而言，每日勞心勞力、營營役役上班，為的只是月尾出糧的一刻。不過，開支太多、人工太少；打工仔只能邊上班邊埋怨人工太低，或是想盡辦法增加收入。<br />\n不過統計處最新數字顯示，現時港人收入中位數為1.5萬元，即假如你月入1.5萬元，收入已經比全港一半人還要多。而假如你月入3萬或以上，你的月入已經是全港收入最高的2成人。<br />\n另外，若以家庭為單位，月入4萬元或以上，你已經是全港收入最高的30%住戶；不過要真正成為本港收入最高的10%，則要年收入過百萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/447370/xlarge/20c77f64d7262d5a55612fcac2da98fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F447370%2Fxlarge%2F20c77f64d7262d5a55612fcac2da98fc.jpg&h=6e20fddf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2bcaa4ec03d724a27097dccb76c0d197a0442af","tid":137501,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />失業"},{"pid":"af0135802ac67161ed81170db5c4e0e6af5da52d","tid":137501,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:46:35.000Z","msg":"LIN登FG生已在22%"},{"pid":"a4d39a503a0f9ad101686a971f8b88050423d94b","tid":137501,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:53:34.000Z","msg":"低過中位數<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869aa7c55c79b1d38d095b14716d1e45cce2815b","tid":137501,"uid":59567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:56:24.000Z","msg":"係度問人工咪個個話幅圖6.8%以上分唔到唔知點答"},{"pid":"8efdd5024cadfd8e09bafee71cd2b6134750b36e","tid":137501,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:04:08.000Z","msg":"36.5k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望下年有40k啦"},{"pid":"d67d